6584:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi2.c **** /*!
6585:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi2.c ****  * @brief This internal API reads the user-defined bytes of data from the given
6586:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi2.c ****  * register address of auxiliary sensor in manual mode.
6587:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi2.c ****  */
