8712:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi2.c **** /*!
8713:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi2.c ****  * @brief This internal API is used to move the data index ahead of the
8714:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi2.c ****  * current_frame_length parameter when unnecessary FIFO data appears while
8715:Core/Src/bmi270/bmi2.c ****  * extracting the user specified data.
